Well, that's bad.

00:17:33.388 --> 00:17:34.930
Because you get collisions.

00:17:34.930 --> 00:17:37.520
So you have to do it
very carefully, for sure.

00:17:37.520 --> 00:17:39.770
GARY GENSLER: So, Eric, did
you have something to add?

00:17:39.770 --> 00:17:43.670
AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE]
But actually,

00:17:43.670 --> 00:17:46.840
the main point of your
