it's actually
collision resistant.

00:18:16.060 --> 00:18:19.110
AUDIENCE: The point, the
really important point,

00:18:19.110 --> 00:18:20.142
it comes to biometrics.

00:18:20.142 --> 00:18:21.100
AUDIENCE: That's right.

00:18:21.100 --> 00:18:21.450
That's right.

00:18:21.450 --> 00:18:23.770
And then the question is,
