their entire identity.

00:18:54.680 --> 00:18:57.620
So I like the idea of
hash somebody's identity,

00:18:57.620 --> 00:18:59.210
hashing a person.

00:18:59.210 --> 00:19:01.570
But I don't think it's
just hashing their eye

00:19:01.570 --> 00:19:02.830
