00:19:08.622 --> 00:19:10.540
It just needs to map
everybody to some number.

00:19:10.540 --> 00:19:12.430
And when you come back,
it needs to figure out

00:19:12.430 --> 00:19:14.260
which number you are or
if you're a new number.

00:19:14.260 --> 00:19:15.130
That's all you need.

00:19:15.130 --> 00:19:16.453
And then, problem solved.

00:19:16.453 --> 00:19:18.370
And then by the way,
personal data attributes,

00:19:18.370 --> 00:19:19.952
you just link those
to those numbers.

00:19:19.952 --> 00:19:21.160
It's not a difficult problem.

00:19:21.160 --> 00:19:23.050
It's an orthogonal problem.

00:19:23.050 --> 00:19:24.320
You solve that [INAUDIBLE]

00:19:24.320 --> 00:19:26.620
GARY GENSLER: So
