headline that says something

00:30:56.070 --> 00:30:58.153
about some important things,
like tomorrow there's

00:30:58.153 --> 00:31:00.057
going to be a snow storm.

00:31:00.057 --> 00:31:01.890
Obviously you want to
know if you're dealing

00:31:01.890 --> 00:31:03.015
with the authentic website.

00:31:03.015 --> 00:31:05.012
That seems to me the problem.

00:31:05.012 --> 00:31:06.220
