00:31:36.583 --> 00:31:39.000
a signature over every piece
of information they send you.

00:31:39.000 --> 00:31:40.350
And you verify it
against their public key,

00:31:40.350 --> 00:31:42.410
which in turn you verified it
from a certificate authority.

00:31:42.410 --> 00:31:44.743
GARY GENSLER: If you remember
