I mean, it's a little bit
like if you forgot your--

00:36:25.540 --> 00:36:28.270
a couple of times you use
a username and password,

00:36:28.270 --> 00:36:30.280
and of course if you
have dual authentication,

00:36:30.280 --> 00:36:34.660
they might send you a notice
to another text message

00:36:34.660 --> 00:36:35.907
or something.

00:36:35.907 --> 00:36:37.490
But if you've forgotten
your password,

00:36:37.490 --> 00:36:40.890
then it's literally backdoor
sort of saying, well,

00:36:40.890 --> 00:36:42.260
to remember your question.

