What's the amount of
cost to those banks

00:41:50.210 --> 00:41:53.000
that they're trying to
move to the merchants

00:41:53.000 --> 00:41:56.300
and thus drop from the
bank's bottom line?

00:41:56.300 --> 00:41:57.800
GARY GENSLER: I
don't have a figure.

