What we know is that the overall
statistics on fraud and credit

00:42:08.640 --> 00:42:13.620
card is, I think, high
teens basis points.

00:42:13.620 --> 00:42:18.160
I can't remember, 15 or 18
basis points but less than 20.

00:42:18.160 --> 00:42:20.030
And it's more than 10.

00:42:20.030 --> 00:42:25.310
So Visa Network charges
270 basis points or so.

00:42:25.310 --> 00:42:29.270
And the fraud part of it's
15 or 18 basis points.

00:42:29.270 --> 00:42:31.636
AUDIENCE: And the issuing
bank gets how much of the 275?

00:42:31.636 --> 00:42:34.465
GARY GENSLER: 200 or so.

