over 100 million customers.

00:43:07.350 --> 00:43:10.080
But then I had to put Facebook
in because it was 50 million.

00:43:10.080 --> 00:43:14.745
But these are just like a dozen
or so really big data breaches.

00:43:17.860 --> 00:43:20.920
There are so many data
breaches in 2018 alone

00:43:20.920 --> 00:43:23.230
that you couldn't list
them on a page like this.

00:43:23.230 --> 00:43:26.950
This is the last five years of
100 million people or more data

00:43:26.950 --> 00:43:28.300
breaches.

00:43:28.300 --> 00:43:30.810
So there's a problem
here in cyber secure.

00:43:30.810 --> 00:43:31.810
And this is just the US.

00:43:34.732 --> 00:43:37.600
Brotish, didn't
the Indian system--

00:43:37.600 --> 00:43:40.630
AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE]
more than a billion.

00:43:40.630 --> 00:43:43.840
GARY GENSLER: 1.1
